Title: Blockheads
Detail: Blockheads are among the earliest NFTs in blockchain history. They exist on Namecoin, the first fork of Bitcoin. Some early crypto users utilized an app called Onename to lock their profiles into the blockchain forever. In total less than 50 Blockheads were created. They are one of the first profile picture NFT collectables and can be seen as the precursor of Cryptopunks.
